OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy but with the
OL,6,Fchance of some bright spells,
OL,7,Fespecially for a time this afternoon
OL,8,Fto the east of the Pennines. Later
OL,9,Fcloud will thicken, bringing some
OL,10,Fpatchy light rain, especially across
OL,11,Fwestern hills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Ffor many places, especially across the
OL,15,FPennines where some heavier bursts
OL,16,Fmany occur and hill fog will develop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
