PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F164A1783048683
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy with hill fog across
OL,6,Fthe Pennines, and light rain gradually
OL,7,Feasing. Elsewhere early patchy light
OL,8,Frain fades, leaving large amounts of
OL,9,Fcloud but with some bright spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fand breezy for much of the period with
OL,14,Fspells of rain at times, mostly
OL,15,Faffecting western hills with drier
OL,16,Fconditions further east. Temperatures
OL,17,Fgradually creeping up, becoming rather
OL,18,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
